aLookup.color && <span style={{ color: INK5, fontWeight: 500 }}> \u00b7 {placaLookup.color}</span>}\n                          </div>\n                        </div>\n                        <button\n                          type=\"button\"\n                          onClick={() => {\n                            handleChange(\"brand\", placaLookup.marca);\n                            handleChange(\"model\", placaLookup.modelo);\n                          }}\n                          style={{\n                            display: \"inline-flex\", alignItems: \"center\", gap: 4,\n                            height: 28, padding: \"0 12px\", borderRadius: 6,\n                            border: `1px solid ${APTO}`, background: \"#fff\", color: APTO,\n                            fontSize: \"0.75rem\", fontWeight: 700,\n                            cursor: \"pointer\", fontFamily: \"inherit\", flexShrink: 0,\n                          }}\n                        >\n                          Aplicar marca y modelo\n                        </button>\n                      </div>\n                    );\n                  })", "is_member_call": false, "source_file": "D:\\Proyectos\\Sistema Sfit\\sfit-web\\src\\app\\(dashboard)\\vehiculos\\[id]\\page.tsx", "source_location": "L619"}, {"caller_nid": "id_page_vehiculodetallepage", "callee": "map", "is_member_call": true, "source_file": "D:\\Proyectos\\Sistema Sfit\\sfit-web\\src\\app\\(dashboard)\\vehiculos\\[id]\\page.tsx", "source_location": "L696"}, {"caller_nid": "id_page_vehiculodetallepage", "callee": "String", "is_member_call": false, "source_file": "D:\\Proyectos\\Sistema Sfit\\sfit-web\\src\\app\\(dashboard)\\vehiculos\\[id]\\page.tsx", "source_location": "L741"}, {"caller_nid": "id_page_vehiculodetallepage", "callee": "map", "is_member_call": true, "source_file": "D:\\Proyectos\\Sistema Sfit\\sfit-web\\src\\app\\(dashboard)\\vehiculos\\[id]\\page.tsx", "source_location": "L787"}, {"caller_nid": "id_page_vehiculodetal